{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-01928/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-01928"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:19:28"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["establishing shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A wall separates a dimly-lit hallway and a door which opens into a bedroom."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-01928","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-01928"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1/8e5afd44-a6fb-4543-b8e0-e98411f7783e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T15:14:37.847Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In this shot, the cool blue contrasts with the warm golden light. Together, the colors represent the tension in Reynolds, as well as the one that plagues Reynolds and Alma, between reserved English coolness and energetic life.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:665.9471365638766,589.7687224669604,1045.3193832599118,382.65418502202624"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1/9fad16e2-b808-4b4b-a51b-744deedc9a63","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T15:14:49.365Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>If the golden light represents the possible dynamism of Alma, this connection is only made more explicit by the wall decorations featuring an outdoor scene. She will get Reynolds to open up.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01928/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1394.31718061674,341.0132158590307,371.4207048458152,149.38325991189447"}}}]}]}]}